{"tid":2163016,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉企圖搶警霰彈槍　16歲男生被加控暴動","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T12:35:23.000Z","uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f0142ee33cd743b868fa907557c5d13de5ad00f5","tid":2163016,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"16歲男學生涉嫌於去年12月底，在上水廣場企圖搶警員的霰彈槍，他本來被控襲警、拒捕和搶劫三罪，案件今（18日）於粉嶺法院再訊時，控方修訂控罪並加控他暴動，並將案轉介往區域法院審理。被告須9月8日到區院答辯，押後期間他獲准以10萬元現金保釋。<br />\n控方修訂控罪後，被告現被控一項暴動罪、一項襲警、兩項拒捕及一項企圖無牌管有槍械罪。控罪指他於去年12月28日，在上水廣場外天橋參與暴動並襲擊編號20614的警員。<br />\n他另被控於同日在上水廣場二樓大堂抗拒編號20614及24201的警員執行職務，以及企圖無牌管有一支警用霰彈槍。<br />\n<br />\n是日笑話精選.......香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75fcec332706138c789419b88ab9ab21f6f8aa9","tid":2163016,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:22:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/viennarosee/status/1270147885233913856?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fviennarosee%2Fstatus%2F1270147885233913856%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5g3kfWbBCvxMfTTNG0K1D1Y%3D&h=1e7c9841\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fviennarosee%2Fstatus%2F1270147885233913856%3Fs%3D21&h=1dad673f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/viennarosee/status/1270147885233913856?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75348c1236424a2612db93495cb15b412cca9a59","tid":2163016,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"搶唔到點算管有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8bbf21156e4787372473cb34fada6032d4e7e8","tid":2163016,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src